        <header class="about-hero">
            <span class="about-subtitle">Our Philosophy</span>
            <h1 class="about-title">We Build Homes Worth Living In</h1>
            <p class="about-lead">
                Homes that adapt to your lifestyle, not the other way around.
                Designed for comfort, built for long-term value. We believe that homes should
                reflect how people live, grow, and connect—making functionality, space, and
                long-term comfort central to every project.
            </p>
        </header>

        <section class="founder-section">
            <div class="founder-container">

                <div class="founder-img-wrapper">
                    <img src="/images/owner-image.png" alt="Founder" class="founder-photo">
                    <div class="founder-decor"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="founder-content">
                    <span class="about-subtitle">About the Founder</span>
                    <h2>The Visionary</h2>

                    <div class="founder-text">
                        <p>
                            With nearly 300 independent houses successfully delivered, the founder brings decades of
                            hands-on experience in residential construction. After building a strong foundation through
                            independent home projects, he has now ventured into the Hyderabad residential market with a
                            clear purpose: to create better living spaces, not just buildings.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            His approach is deeply rooted in adapting design and craftsmanship to the unique needs of
                            each
                            city, community, and family. A visionary leader with a strong ethical foundation, he is
                            as a builder who listens, adapts, and delivers.
                        </p>
                        <p class="founder-quote">
                            "Development goes beyond construction—it’s about creating neighborhoods where people truly
                            belong."
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

