        <section class="vision-section">
            <div class="vision-container">
                <span class="about-subtitle" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">Our Approach</span>
                <h2>Understanding How You Live</h2>
                <p>
                    Before laying a single brick, we conducted in-depth research into how people in the community live,
                    grow, and use their homes. We studied existing residential layouts, evolving lifestyles, and the
                    aspirations of families in the area. This understanding became the foundation of our design
                    approach.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Whether it is the functional flow of <strong>Sai Saman Diamond</strong> or the timeless elegance of
                    <strong>Sai Saman Crown</strong>, every layout decision balances openness, privacy, and
                    functionality.
                    Our result is a residence that feels intuitive and comfortable—a home that fits the lifestyle
                    of the community, rather than forcing a generic design into it.
